high_descs: Turn left then take a step to your left then walk past the counter and chair to your right and when you get past them turn right and walk between the two yellow chairs then turn right.
Pick up the green cup that's in front of you.
Turn right and walk past the counter to your left and when you get past it turn left ad walk to the fridge.
Chill the cup in the fridge then get it back out and close the door.
Turn left and walk to the microwave.
Put the cup in the microwave.
anns.task_desc: Put a cold cup in the microwave.

high_descs: Turn around and walk around the counter to your right, and go between the two chairs, at the counter.
Pick up the green cup, to the right of the fry pan, on the counter.
Turn to your right and go back around the counter to your left and to the refrigerator.
Place the green cup on the bottom shelf, in front of the potato, in the refrigerator, wait a moment for the cup to chill, then remove the cup from the refrigerator.
Turn to your left and go to the microwave, on the counter across from you.
Place the green cup in the microwave.
anns.task_desc: Put a cold cup in the microwave.

high_descs: Turn left, move around to the other side of the counter, turn right to face the counter.
Pick up the green cup on the counter.
Bring the cup to the fridge on the right.
Chill the cup on the fridge.
Bring the chilled cup to the microwave to the left.
Put the chilled cup in the microwave.
anns.task_desc: Put a chilled cup in the microwave.
